'''薩摩亞全國聯賽'''（Samoa National League）是大洋洲島國[[薩摩亞|薩摩亞]]國內最高級別足球聯賽。容量3500人的{{le|National Soccer Stadium, Apia||国家足球场}}是全國聯賽的唯一球場。<ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/nov/10/which-stadiums-home-to-most-champions Which stadiums are home to the most champions?] at The Knowledge, Guardian Newspapers</ref>

